aima.core.environment.nqueens

Class NQueensBoard

  • java.lang.Object
    • aima.core.environment.nqueens.NQueensBoard

  • public class NQueensBoard
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a quadratic board with a matrix of squares on which queens can be placed (only one per square) and moved.
    Author:
    Ravi Mohan, Ruediger Lunde
